@PomoApp.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5194

### Get timer status
GET {{PomoApp.Api_HostAddress}}/timer/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Start timer
POST {{PomoApp.Api_HostAddress}}/timer/start

###

### Pause timer
POST {{PomoApp.Api_HostAddress}}/timer/pause

###

### Reset timer
POST {{PomoApp.Api_HostAddress}}/timer/reset

###

### Skip to next phase
POST {{PomoApp.Api_HostAddress}}/timer/skip

###

### Get settings
GET {{PomoApp.Api_HostAddress}}/settings
Accept: application/json

###

### Update settings
PUT {{PomoApp.Api_HostAddress}}/settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workMinutes": 25,
  "breakMinutes": 5,
  "longBreakMinutes": 15,
  "sessionsBeforeLongBreak": 4
}

###
